\li{Platform-specific tools}
}

\p{For complete details on each area including what I'll check, analyze, and recommend, see [ASSESSMENT_AREAS.md](resources/ASSESSMENT_AREAS.md).}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Example Output}
\p{When the analysis is complete, you'll receive comprehensive guidance covering:}

\ul{
\li{System documentation with plain English descriptions}
\li{Architectural diagrams and documentation gaps}
\li{Architecture analysis (on-chain/off-chain, upgradeability, proxies)}
\li{Implementation review (functions, inheritance, events, pitfalls)}
\li{Dependencies and testing evaluation}
\li{Prioritized recommendations (CRITICAL, HIGH, MEDIUM, LOW)}
\li{Overall assessment and path to production}
}

\p{For a complete example analysis report, see [EXAMPLE_REPORT.md](resources/EXAMPLE_REPORT.md).}
}

